_description:
Gospel, ‘Dominica in oct. Epiphanie: Evangelium secundum
Mattheum’, in the ‘expanded’ Northern Homily Cycle

BLHar4196.First Lines: Ihesu crist come out of galileffro nazareth his awin cete…
BLHar4196.Last Lines: …Þe trinite þus wald apereÞe sacrament so till vs at lere
BLHar4196.Note: Preceded by Latin “UEnit Ihesu crist a galilea & cetera.”
BLHar4196.Attributed Title: DOminica infra octava Epiphanie Euangelium secundum Matheum (rubric, f. 31rb)
BLHar4196.Editions:
Nevanlinna,  Sara. 
             The Northern Homily Cycle: The Expanded Version in MSS Harley 4196 and Cotton Tiberius E.vii.
             3 vols. 
             Memoires de la Societé Neophilologique de Helsinki.
         Helsinki. 38 (1972); 41 (1973); and 43 (1984): I.268-272.
